            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Felix <lb n="2"/>Aurunculeianus <expan><abbr>aed</abbr><ex>ilis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>ob honorem aedilitatis signum <lb n="4"/>Marsyae quod ex HS <expan><abbr>IICCCC</abbr><ex>duobus milibus quadringentis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ummum</ex></expan> cum <lb n="5"/>legitima <expan><abbr>sum</abbr><ex>ma</ex></expan> taxaverat <expan><abbr>adiect</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>amplius <expan><abbr>pec</abbr><ex>unia</ex></expan> posuit et <expan><abbr>dedic</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>idemq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> primus ludos dedit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite befinden sich Einlassungen zur Verdübelung der Statue.</p>
